metadata.name: Dream #1 The Scarf Girl
metadata.description:
The girl here in the picture looking directly into my soul questioning me do you see my beauty or do u see my pain? Then I couldn’t reply because I wanted to project the same thing with the viewers too. She is beautiful, and also she had a few dreams. And when I asked her about her dreams She smiled with a little hesitation & said Brother If you can help please make our story, please let us have a home and help us in having our studies. 
I have questioned myself, I wasn’t broke but I was questioned. So, I wanted to make this picture speak to someone who can help. 
Photographer Name: Arun Kumar Nalimela
Edition: 1/1 
Dimensions: 5304 × 7952
